Saka dhora saini yaive iri yemari.

0:24:26.100,0:24:29.500
Waivimba kuti chero ukawana mari unenge wave pakanaka.

0:24:29.500,0:24:33.240
Zvese zvako zvaive zvekuwana mari, kusangana nevarume, kurara navo nekuwana mari.

0:24:33.240,0:24:34.020
hongu.

0:24:34.020,0:24:36.480
Tiudze, mari iyi waishandisa kuita chii?

0:24:36.480,0:24:37.980
Wai shandisa kuita chimwe chinhu chine basa here?

0:24:37.980,0:24:49.680
Taishandisa mari kutenga doro muma Kirabhu, kutenga zvipfeko ne kufambisa kuenda kunzvimbo dzakanaka kunozvifadza.

0:24:49.680,0:24:53.280
Hauna kana kumbokwanisa kushandisa mari yacho kuita chinhu chine musoro.

0:24:53.280,0:24:58.080
Waingoishandisa kunwa, kuputa , kutenga hembe zvadaro mari yacho yaibva yapera.

0:24:58.080,0:24:59.520
Hongu.

0:24:59.520,0:25:04.620
Mukusangana ne varume, zvii zvimwe zvawakatanga kuita kuvarume ivavo.

0:25:04.620,0:25:07.740
kuitira kuti uwane mari?

0:25:07.740,0:25:16.520
Pave nerimwe zuva randaenda pane umwe murume, ndikaona mari patafura; mweya wakaipa waive mandiri wakandiita kuti nditore mari iyoyo

0:25:16.520,0:25:21.840
Kubva musi iwowo wandakaba mari kubva kumurume iyeye, ndakatanga kuba mari kubva kuvarume.

0:25:21.840,0:25:25.560
Hapana pavaigona kuviga mari ndikasapaziva.

0:25:25.560,0:25:29.440
Ndaienda ipapo kunotora mari iyoyo.

0:25:29.440,0:25:33.800
Shamwari dzangu dzaiti pane mari yashaikwa.

0:25:33.800,0:25:39.100
Havai zvibvuma kuti ndini ndaive ndichitora mari; ndairatidza semusvinu zvakanyanya

0:25:39.100,0:25:41.740
Vaitanga kupomera umwe munhu.

0:25:41.740,0:25:48.460
Mushure mekurara ne varume, vaiku bhadhara asi waivabira zvakare?

0:25:48.460,0:25:49.300
Hongu.

0:25:49.300,0:25:51.220
Uye havana kumbokufungira kuti ndiwe waiva bira.

0:25:51.220,0:25:52.040
Hongu.

0:25:52.040,0:25:55.400
Tiudze, apo wainderera mberi nemararamiro iwawo...

0:25:55.400,0:25:58.500
Unoreva here kuti wakabva pamba penyu uine makore 14?

0:25:58.500,0:26:00.380
Hongu, ndakabva pamba.

0:26:00.380,0:26:05.900
Vainditsvaga asi handina kuvapa adhiresi yepandaigara.

0:26:05.900,0:26:10.720
Kubva pamakore 14 wakabva pamba ukatanga kufamba famba, uchirara nevarume kuti uwane mari

0:26:10.720,0:26:12.100
nekufamba famba ne shamwari dzako?

0:26:12.100,0:26:13.120
Hongu.

0:26:13.120,0:26:18.260
Nguva yese iyo waienda kukhirabhu - chii chawaita kuti ukwezve varume, avo vaizoda nezvako?

0:26:18.260,0:26:20.500
Ndinogona kutamba zvakanaka.

0:26:20.500,0:26:26.980
Apo ndaitanga kutamba mu kirabhu, varume vaizorwira kuti vave neni.

0:26:26.980,0:26:33.540
Titaurire, wakambopfuura nemune zvimwe zvinhu zvausingazo kanganwa zvakaitika apo waiita zve chipfambi izvi?

0:26:33.540,0:26:36.320
Zvichida wakasangana ne umwe murume aida kuita chimwe chinhu kwauri?

0:26:36.320,0:26:38.340
Sekutaura kwaita mukoma wako - zviri maeranao netsika dzacho ?

0:26:38.340,0:26:40.860
Imhandoi dzawa kasangana nadzo panguva iyoyo?

0:26:40.860,0:26:44.140
Hongu, ndine zvimwe zvakaitika mukusangana izvo ndisinga kanganwe.

0:26:44.140,0:26:51.560
Pane musi apo shamwari dzangu nhatu dzakashevedzwa kuti dziende nevasikana, ndaive umwe wavo

0:26:51.560,0:26:57.260
Taive mumotokari, asi pekupedzisira ndakazozviona ndiri musango.

0:26:57.260,0:26:59.820
Tose taive tisina kupfeka, kusara kwe bhurukwa re mukati ne bhodhi.

0:26:59.820,0:27:04.800
Vakasunga vhudzi redu vakaisa mutengo pamisoro yedu waita 500,000 Naira

0:27:04.800,0:27:11.380
Ndakafunga kuti ndaive ndakuzofa zuva iroro, ndakanamata kuti Mwari andiregerere zvivi zvangu.

0:27:11.380,0:27:14.740
Ndaingo namata

0:27:14.740,0:27:18.380
Apo ndakadzoka, mai vangu vakati usiku humwe chete hwo vakanga varota vachina kundiuraya;

0:27:18.380,0:27:21.060
vainamata

0:27:21.060,0:27:22.880
Ndakanamata.

0:27:22.880,0:27:25.340
Varume vacho vaiva vakuru kuru.

0:27:25.340,0:27:32.160
Kwaive ne misoro yevanhu, vaana vacheche, mabhegi echikoro, maunifomu; zvese zvaivepo.

0:27:32.160,0:27:35.120
Musikana akanga atiudza ne motokari akati misoro yedu yaive isina kunaka,

0:27:35.120,0:27:36.940
nekuti taive tavaitisa munyama.

0:27:36.940,0:27:40.540
Mushure mepakati peusiku , taimhanya ne sango; kwainaya

0:27:40.540,0:27:42.160
Ndiko kupukunyuka kwatakaita.

0:27:42.160,0:27:47.780
Mukadzi wepamusika akatipa machira kuti tisunge apo taidzokera kwedu

0:27:47.780,0:27:52.020
Ndizvo zvawakasangana nazvo apo waive muchipfambi

0:27:52.020,0:27:56.640
Wakambosangana nezvakada kufanana naizvozvo here muhotera?

0:27:56.640,0:28:04.360
Ndakasangana ne umwe murume akati iye mufundisi.

0:28:04.360,0:28:10.500
Akati ndaive ndakanaka, uye ndaive akafanira kuita basa iroro kwaari.

0:28:10.500,0:28:16.140
Akati akanga ari mufundisi, kuti aiva ne chirongwa uko aizoparidza uye nekuona zviratidzo.

0:28:16.140,0:28:19.840
Akandiratidza kune vamwe vasikana vaishanda naye.

0:28:19.840,0:28:21.060
Aizondiudza zvekuita.

0:28:21.060,0:28:27.400
Taizoenda kuchechi uye vasikana vaizondisvitsa pedyo nevarume vane mari.

0:28:27.400,0:28:31.520
Ndaizotaura ne murume, ndopihwa nhamba dze foni yake nezita rake.

0:28:31.520,0:28:34.260
Ndaizovaudza nezve murume iyeye.

0:28:34.260,0:28:37.360
Mufundisi aizoenda mugungano onyepera kuziva murume uyu seku profita

0:28:37.360,0:28:39.320
Aizomuudza kuti auye kwaari obva amuudza nhamba dze foni yake.

0:28:39.320,0:28:44.320
Aizoita mari yakawanda kubva kumurume iyeye.

0:28:44.320,0:28:49.880
Ndihwo hurongwa hwe murume aizviti mufundisi, kuti waizoenda kuchechi

0:28:49.880,0:28:56.660
wo shamwaridzana ne umwe munhu ikoko, wotora zvese zvemunhu iyeye, wopa murume iyeye, paruzhinji iye aizoita

0:28:56.660,0:29:00.200
se arikuprofita nezvazvo kuitira kuti awane mari kubva kune murume iyeye.

0:29:00.200,0:29:02.620
Hongu.

0:29:02.620,0:29:06.860
Mukuita basa iroro kwaari, akafamba kuenda kunze kwenyika.

0:29:06.860,0:29:14.000
Paakadzoka, ndakamuudza kuti ndakanga ndisipo; akati aizowana umwe munhu.

0:29:14.000,0:29:19.100
Wakamboedza kurega mararamiro emhando iyi here usati wauya pa Synagogue?

0:29:19.100,0:29:22.980
Hongu, ndakamboedza kuzvirega asi ndakatadza.

0:29:22.980,0:29:28.780
Apo ndairega, ndaidzoka nezvinhu zvangu kumba asi zvinhu zvaive zvisina kumira mushe.

0:29:28.780,0:29:32.540
Paive pasina mari.

0:29:32.540,0:29:38.580
Mweya wakaipa waindibvunza kuti uri kuitei pano, une nzara uye hauna zvekupfeka;

0:29:38.580,0:29:42.260
Ndobva ndadzokera kumigwagwa zvakare.

0:29:42.260,0:29:45.600
Zvakanaka, tiri kunyatso nzwisisa kubva kune hanzvadzi yedu kuti chii change chichiitika mu upenyu hwake aine makore 18 chete.

0:29:45.600,0:29:48.260
Izvi ndizvo zvaakapfuura mazviri.

0:29:48.260,0:29:52.160
Tinotenda Mwari Samasimba kuti uri pano nhasi ne mukoma wako se chapupu ku ukuru hwa Mwari.

0:29:52.160,0:29:57.960
Tiudze, chii chakaitika apo wakauya pa SCOAN ne mukoma wako.

0:29:57.960,0:30:02.040
Gore rapera muna  November, mukoma wangu akauya pa SCOAN achibva angamuchira Anoiting Water.

0:30:02.040,0:30:03.660
akauya nayo kumba.

0:30:03.660,0:30:07.020
Akati munhu wese anofanira kushandisa Anoiting Water (Mvura ine zodzo)

0:30:07.020,0:30:12.620
Apo ndakashandisa Anoiting Water pandiri, ndakaita dzungu

0:30:12.620,0:30:19.400
Shamwari dzangu dzaiuya dzichindidana kuti tiende kumafaro asi ndaivaudza kuti ndaive ndisingade kuenda

0:30:19.400,0:30:28.620
Nguva zhinji pandairota, ndaiona Mafundisi vachindiudza kuti handiyo nzira yekunakidzwa ne upenyu hwako.

0:30:28.620,0:30:32.400
Ndakaronga zvekuuya ku SCOAN.

0:30:32.400,0:30:35.960
Pandaiuya ku SCOAN nzira dzese dzaive dzichidzivirirwa, taive takaronga  kuuya muna December

0:30:35.960,0:30:36.980
asi paive pasina mari.

0:30:36.980,0:30:39.580
Hapana kwandaigona kuenda; paive pasina mari.

0:30:39.580,0:30:43.660
Mushure ma December, nguva ye Goredzva, ndakati tinofanira kuenda ku SCOAN.

0:30:43.660,0:30:47.820
Pamutsetse wekunamatira, mukoma wangu aka dzikunurwa.

0:30:47.820,0:30:52.600
Apo Wiseman akaswedera pedyo neni, paive nemoto pose paaari; ndakatadza kumutarisa.

0:30:52.600,0:30:57.920
Ndakange ndisiri ini, kusvikira ndasimuka kubva pasi.

0:30:57.920,0:31:01.500
Titaurire hanzvadzi, kubva zvawakanunurwa - uchapupu hwako ndehwei?

0:31:01.500,0:31:02.660
Upenyu hwako hwashanduka sei?

0:31:02.660,0:31:03.840
Upenyu hwangu hwakanaka.

0:31:03.840,0:31:08.500
Ndinogona kuona chinhu asi handichina chido chekuti ndichibe.

0:31:08.500,0:31:09.700
Ndiripo hangu.

0:31:09.700,0:31:13.520
Shamwari dzangu dzinondifonera dzichindibvunza kuti ndaivepi asi ndaivaudza kuti vasazondifonera zvakare.

0:31:13.520,0:31:14.700
nekuti handisisiri mazviri.

0:31:14.700,0:31:19.060
Shamwari yangu yakati nekuda kwekuti ini ndakachinja, naye  anoda kuchinjawo, akati aizouya kuSCOAN

0:31:19.060,0:31:22.480
nokuti upenyu hwaairarama akange asisa hude.

0:31:22.480,0:31:26.180
Unoreva shamwari dzako dzaive mu hunhu hwawairarama, nokuda kwe ku chinja kwe upenyu hwako vakati

0:31:26.180,0:31:27.700
vakuda kuuyawo ku SCOAN?

0:31:27.700,0:31:29.360
hongu.

0:31:29.360,0:31:34.680
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe kuna Jesu Kristu nokuda kwe shanduko yakanakisa.

0:31:34.680,0:31:38.500
Ko mweya we ruchiva, waikusundudzira kuti urare nevarume?

0:31:38.500,0:31:39.400
Uri sei iko zvino?

0:31:39.400,0:31:40.820
Uchine mweya uya waikusundidzira?

0:31:40.820,0:31:42.140
Kwete.

0:31:42.140,0:31:43.880
Wange uchirara sei?

0:31:43.880,0:31:50.900
Kwave ne mwedzi miviri kubva pa dzikinuro yangu uye handisisina chido chekusangana ne varume

0:31:50.900,0:31:52.200
Mbiri kuna Mwari weMasimbaose.

0:31:52.200,0:31:55.840
Tinotenda Jesu Kristu nekuda kwe hupenyu hwako ne hwe mukoma wako.

0:31:55.840,0:31:59.840
Ndinofunga uri pachinzvimbo chekuti upe mazano kamwe zvakare kune vechiduku pasi rose.

0:31:59.840,0:32:04.000
Chii chaizvo chaunoda kupa mazano kune vechiduku vari kukuona iye zvino?

0:32:04.000,0:32:10.660
Vechidiki vanoziva kuti varombo, ndinoda kuvaudza kuti kana umwe munhu achivanyengedza kuti vaende naye

0:32:10.660,0:32:16.260
kunoita mari, mari yaunoita, hapana chaunowana pazviri, hapana chaunogona kuita nayo.

0:32:16.260,0:32:22.400
Kana vakaudza kuti uende ku na'nga, vari kuisa mimwe minyama mu upenyu hwako;

0:32:22.400,0:32:25.860
hapana chavanogona kukubatsira nacho.

0:32:25.860,0:32:28.920
Saka, uri kuraira vanhu kuti vambundire Jesu Kristu...?

0:32:28.920,0:32:30.880
Hongu.

0:32:30.880,0:32:36.960
Tinodaira kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

0:32:36.960,0:32:43.360
Tinya apa kuti unyorese kupupurira zvakawanda pamusoro pesimba ra Mwari pabasa munguva yatiri nhasi

0:32:43.360,0:32:49.700
kuti ugare uri pamusoro pezvichagoburwa zvehuporofita, rudzikinuro,mharidzo nezvapupu

0:32:49.700,0:32:52.560
zvinobva ku Synagogue Church of All Nations.

